<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Cancellation</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your custom styling here */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>Booking Cancellation for {{serviceName}} on {{date}}</h2>

<p>Dear {{clientName}},</p>

<p>We regret to inform you that your booking with the following details has been canceled:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Client Name:</strong> {{clientName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Service:</strong> {{serviceName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Staff Member:</strong> {{staffName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</li>
    <li><strong>Time:</strong> {{time}}</li>
    <li><strong>Total Amount:</strong> {{totalAmount}}</li>
    <li><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</li>
    <li><strong>Notes:</strong> {{notes}}</li>
</ul>

<p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding this cancellation, please contact us at {{adminMail}}. We apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused.</p>

<p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>

<p>Best Regards,<br>
    {{companyName}} Team<br>
    {{adminMail}}</p>
</body>
</html>
